1
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:36,879
Honey!

2
00:01:36,879 --> 00:01:38,000
Somebody, help!

3
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:39,480
Something's wrong!

4
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:40,599
Help, somebody!

5
00:01:41,159 --> 00:01:42,200
What happened?

6
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:43,560
What's going on here?

7
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:45,560
He took the medicine and started vomiting blood!

8
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:46,920
Calm down for a moment.

9
00:01:48,319 --> 00:01:49,120
What is this?

10
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:49,799
Honey!

11
00:01:49,799 --> 00:01:50,840
You're Liu Tiezhu.

12
00:01:52,599 --> 00:01:54,239
Who altered this prescription?

13
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,319
The medicine didn't match the symptoms.

14
00:01:57,319 --> 00:01:59,120
I just made a few changes.

15
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:00,439
What did you say?

16
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:02,319
You "just made a few changes"?

17
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:05,239
Do you know who wrote this prescription?

18
00:02:05,239 --> 00:02:08,319
This was written by Pharmacist Zhu himself!

19
00:02:08,719 --> 00:02:10,240
You, a mere apprentice,

20
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:11,400
have some nerve!

21
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:12,439
Has your audacity gone through the roof?

22
00:02:12,439 --> 00:02:13,159
You!

23
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:15,879
The medicine didn't fit the illness.

24
00:02:15,879 --> 00:02:16,879
The patient was dying.

25
00:02:16,879 --> 00:02:18,919
Was I supposed to just watch him die?

26
00:02:18,919 --> 00:02:19,879
You!

27
00:02:19,879 --> 00:02:20,479
What's going on?

28
00:02:21,919 --> 00:02:23,360
Pharmacist Zhu,

29
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:25,000
he altered your prescription without permission,

30
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:26,280
causing the patient to vomit blood.

31
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:27,479
The situation is critical!

32
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,520
You recklessly changed the medicine,

33
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:30,639
and if something happens to the patient,

34
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:31,840
can you bear the consequences?

35
00:02:32,879 --> 00:02:34,560
You're completely out of control!

36
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:35,439
Reckless and arrogant!

37
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:41,639
Saving lives always comes first, no matter what.

38
00:02:43,319 --> 00:02:45,199
You guys are ridiculous.

39
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:48,199
This is a place for healing and saving lives.

40
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:51,080
Instead of worrying about the patient's safety,

41
00:02:51,080 --> 00:02:52,520
you're standing here lecturing about rules?

42
00:02:54,039 --> 00:02:54,439
You!

43
00:02:56,759 --> 00:02:58,000
I'm sorry!

44
00:02:58,000 --> 00:02:59,039
Pharmacist Zhu, I'm sorry!

45
00:02:59,039 --> 00:02:59,919
He's new to the apothecary.

46
00:02:59,919 --> 00:03:00,719
He doesn't know the rules.

47
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:05,000
Wuming, apologize, quickly!

48
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:06,479
Otherwise, when Director Ye arrives,

49
00:03:06,479 --> 00:03:07,960
she'll surely kick you out of the apothecary.

50
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:09,599
Why should I?

51
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:11,159
Why should I apologize

52
00:03:11,159 --> 00:03:12,360
to a bunch of quacks who prescribed the wrong medicine?

53
00:03:13,199 --> 00:03:14,120
Don't you know?

54
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:16,840
An apprentice has no right to alter a pharmacist's prescription.

55
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:17,639
And Director Ye, she...

56
00:03:17,639 --> 00:03:18,439
Oh, really?

57
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:20,719
This is the first time I've heard

58
00:03:20,719 --> 00:03:21,879
anyone dare to speak this way

59
00:03:21,879 --> 00:03:23,319
about the pharmacists of Tianzi One.

60
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,199
Director Ye!

61
00:03:31,199 --> 00:03:31,960
You're here.

62
00:03:33,199 --> 00:03:34,039
This apprentice here

63
00:03:34,039 --> 00:03:35,000
acted recklessly,

64
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:36,639
altered a prescription without authorization,

65
00:03:36,639 --> 00:03:38,120
and caused the patient to vomit blood.

66
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:39,159
He has no regard for the rules.

67
00:03:39,719 --> 00:03:40,639
He must be fired!

68
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:43,280
What's going on?

69
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,919
You want to fire me?

70
00:03:44,919 --> 00:03:46,639
Shouldn't you also fire this quack who prescribed the wrong medicine,

71
00:03:46,639 --> 00:03:48,879
along with this slacking apothecary master?

72
00:04:09,919 --> 00:04:11,319
How are you feeling now?

73
00:04:20,360 --> 00:04:21,040
I...

74
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:22,399
I...

75
00:04:53,399 --> 00:04:54,600
I...

76
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:56,759
I feel so much better.

77
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:02,480
The tightness in my chest is gone.

78
00:05:06,319 --> 00:05:07,560
Everything's flowing freely.

79
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:09,240
The medicine worked like magic.

80
00:05:10,879 --> 00:05:12,560
I'm really cured.

81
00:05:23,519 --> 00:05:25,519
How strange.

82
00:05:25,519 --> 00:05:27,399
The blood stasis in the patient's chest

83
00:05:28,319 --> 00:05:29,279
actually cleared up.

84
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,759
How could it be so fast?

85
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:34,240
I'm better.

86
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,120
Finally healed.

87
00:05:41,160 --> 00:05:42,240
It really did clear.

88
00:05:50,759 --> 00:05:52,800
Even so,

89
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:56,000
a lowly apprentice altering a prescription without authorization

90
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:57,519
breaks the rules.

91
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:59,680
He must be severely punished.

92
00:06:00,319 --> 00:06:00,879
Director Ye.

93
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:03,800
Or our Tianzi One will fall into chaos.

94
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:10,959
Indeed.

95
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:17,600
You abandoned your post,

96
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:18,439
slacking off,

97
00:06:18,439 --> 00:06:19,279
shirking your duties.

98
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:22,000
Our Tianzi One has no place for someone like you.

99
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:25,319
You can leave.

100
00:06:26,639 --> 00:06:27,920
Director Ye.

101
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:29,800
Let go of me!

102
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:31,319
Director Ye, let me explain!

103
00:06:31,319 --> 00:06:32,319
Give me one chance!

104
00:06:32,319 --> 00:06:34,639
Director Ye! Let go! Director Ye!

105
00:06:40,079 --> 00:06:41,480
Pharmacist Zhu has always been cautious.

106
00:06:42,399 --> 00:06:45,600
His prescriptions are mostly safe and conservative.

107
00:06:46,279 --> 00:06:47,240
He didn't write the wrong prescription.

108
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:49,399
Do you acknowledge this?

109
00:06:51,199 --> 00:06:52,519
If you put it that way,

110
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:54,560
that's fine.

111
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:03,920
Though the new apprentice cured you instantly,

112
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:07,000
we still gave you quite a scare.

113
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,639
Please follow my assistant Xiaoqiu

114
00:07:08,639 --> 00:07:10,199
to receive proper compensation.

115
00:07:11,279 --> 00:07:12,680
Thank you, Director Ye.

116
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,680
Thank you.

117
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:14,800
Sorry for the trouble.

118
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:20,279
Finally cured.

119
00:07:20,279 --> 00:07:21,480
Much better.

120
00:07:25,199 --> 00:07:27,000
As for you,

121
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:28,240
come with me.

122
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,199
Director Ye.

123
00:07:29,199 --> 00:07:30,399
I'm sorry, Wuming.

124
00:07:32,839 --> 00:07:34,120
I'll take responsibility for my own actions.

125
00:07:36,399 --> 00:07:38,360
It's fine. Leave it to me.

126
00:07:46,839 --> 00:07:48,759
You do have genuine skill.

127
00:07:49,639 --> 00:07:50,399
However,

128
00:07:54,279 --> 00:07:57,639
the Xuan Medical Society stands in Qijiang City

129
00:07:58,079 --> 00:07:59,839
relying not only on medical skills,

130
00:08:00,319 --> 00:08:01,319
but also on its rules.

131
00:08:07,759 --> 00:08:09,519
One must know how to be flexible.

132
00:08:09,879 --> 00:08:11,240
We can't just follow the rules

133
00:08:11,959 --> 00:08:13,120
and refuse to save patients, can we?

134
00:08:18,759 --> 00:08:19,839
Without rules,

135
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:22,600
even great skill can't protect you.

136
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:24,680
That being said,

137
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:26,680
congratulations on passing my test.

138
00:08:32,799 --> 00:08:35,759
So that patient was a test?

139
00:08:38,159 --> 00:08:39,240
The people I employ,

140
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:41,639
at the very least,

141
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:43,639
must have their character tested.

142
00:09:08,759 --> 00:09:10,759
Does this person look familiar?

143
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,639
Who is this guy?

144
00:09:14,639 --> 00:09:15,320
Never seen him.

145
00:09:16,759 --> 00:09:17,679
How about now?

146
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:21,120
Well...

147
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:24,840
He's pretty handsome.

148
00:09:27,559 --> 00:09:28,879
The entire Xuan Medical Society

149
00:09:28,879 --> 00:09:30,000
is hunting down this guy,

150
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:32,240
the thief who stole the Zhenhai Jingxin Manual.

151
00:09:32,679 --> 00:09:34,159
What do you mean, "stole"?

152
00:09:34,159 --> 00:09:35,919
I won it fair and square.

153
00:09:35,919 --> 00:09:37,360
Oh, really?

154
00:09:37,360 --> 00:09:38,799
Then you'd better convince them.

155
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:41,960
But who knows if they're as reasonable as me.

156
00:09:42,639 --> 00:09:43,120
You...

157
00:09:47,039 --> 00:09:47,799
I'm sorry, Director Ye.

158
00:09:47,799 --> 00:09:49,279
My attitude was a bit out of line earlier.

159
00:09:49,759 --> 00:09:51,639
We can discuss cooperation.

160
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:56,840
As long as you represent my Qingmu Hall

161
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:59,600
in the upcoming Five Elements Banquet Trial,

162
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:01,200
I'll settle today's incident,

163
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:03,279
and guarantee you a spot in Tianzi One.

164
00:10:04,559 --> 00:10:05,200
Director Ye!

165
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:13,919
The patient is in trouble!

166
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:16,360
Wait for me here.

167
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:36,879
Careful, watch your step.

168
00:10:38,600 --> 00:10:40,000
My father was just fine a moment ago.

169
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:41,600
How did his condition suddenly get worse?

170
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:43,039
Please, try not to worry.

171
00:10:43,519 --> 00:10:44,960
The one treating him inside

172
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:46,320
is from our Xuan Medical Society's Chihuo Hall,

173
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:47,320
Medicine Holder Li Xiangyang.

174
00:10:48,279 --> 00:10:49,279
With Holder Li handling it,

175
00:10:49,279 --> 00:10:50,600
I can finally rest easy.

176
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:52,039
Don't keep standing here like this.

177
00:10:52,039 --> 00:10:53,039
Your body can't take it.

178
00:10:53,039 --> 00:10:54,559
Go rest in the waiting area for now.

179
00:10:54,559 --> 00:10:55,399
All right.

180
00:10:55,399 --> 00:10:56,440
Your father's going to be fine.

181
00:10:56,879 --> 00:10:57,519
Come on.

182
00:10:57,519 --> 00:10:58,000
Take it slow.

183
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:21,679
The patient's body is battling cold and heat at once.

184
00:11:21,679 --> 00:11:22,919
Their qi flow is in chaos.

185
00:11:22,919 --> 00:11:24,120
If we don't regulate the temperature in time,

186
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:25,679
they may fall into shock.

187
00:11:25,679 --> 00:11:27,600
You two, come with me now to get the thermostat.

188
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:29,519
Then use sedatives to stabilize the pulse.

189
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:47,600
Pharmacist Lu

190
00:11:49,759 --> 00:11:50,159
Be careful.

191
00:11:50,159 --> 00:11:50,679
Hold him down.

192
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:00,679
Aren't you the new apprentice from the pharmacy?

193
00:12:00,679 --> 00:12:02,279
Why are you treating a patient without permission?

194
00:12:02,279 --> 00:12:02,879
His qi flow is in chaos.

195
00:12:02,879 --> 00:12:03,840
It needs to be guided immediately.

196
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:05,919
Wuming.

197
00:12:05,919 --> 00:12:06,480
Go shut the door, quick.

198
00:12:06,480 --> 00:12:07,200
I have to save him.

199
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:09,799
You can't. You'd be breaking the rules.

200
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:12,919
His heart-yang is failing.

201
00:12:12,919 --> 00:12:13,720
Liver fire is rising.

202
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:14,360
Once all five organs are out of balance,

203
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:15,480
no one will be able to save him.

204
00:12:15,480 --> 00:12:16,080
Hurry!

205
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:19,320
Holder Li!

206
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:21,559
An apprentice is recklessly treating a patient in the ward!

207
00:12:21,559 --> 00:12:22,840
What?

208
00:12:22,840 --> 00:12:24,200
Bring the equipment up here, now!

209
00:12:29,159 --> 00:12:30,279
Lu Tanxiang!

210
00:12:31,879 --> 00:12:32,720
Don't touch my patient!

211
00:12:44,080 --> 00:12:44,759
Lu Tanxiang!

212
00:12:47,960 --> 00:12:48,559
Lu Tanxiang!

213
00:12:49,200 --> 00:12:50,720
Open the door!

214
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:51,360
Hurry up!

215
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:53,600
The meridians are flowing in reverse.

216
00:12:53,600 --> 00:12:55,159
The qi sea is in turmoil.

217
00:12:55,159 --> 00:12:56,919
Only by channeling qi through phantom needles,

218
00:12:56,919 --> 00:12:59,799
piercing top to bottom straight into the root,

219
00:12:59,799 --> 00:13:02,360
can the qi be restored to its source.

220
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:04,480
Golden Needle Qi Transmission?

221
00:13:04,480 --> 00:13:06,279
You actually know this lost ancient art?

222
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:23,960
Completely drained.

223
00:13:26,360 --> 00:13:28,200
Lu Tanxiang, open this door now!

224
00:13:33,919 --> 00:13:35,120
Who do you think you are?

225
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:35,720
Xiangyang.

226
00:13:35,720 --> 00:13:36,679
How dare you barge into the ward?

227
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:39,600
And who the hell are you?

228
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:46,159
Skilled mystery apprentice saves Miss Lu from danger.

229
00:13:46,159 --> 00:13:47,600
It's you.

230
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:48,639
You country quack.

231
00:13:48,639 --> 00:13:49,399
Xiangyang.

232
00:13:49,399 --> 00:13:51,279
Today I'll make you understand

233
00:13:51,279 --> 00:13:53,080
exactly what "rules" mean.

234
00:13:55,600 --> 00:13:56,720
If you want to argue, take it outside.

235
00:13:56,720 --> 00:13:58,279
Don't disturb the patient's rest here.

236
00:13:58,279 --> 00:13:59,320
Ye Qingxue.

237
00:13:59,320 --> 00:14:01,279
Are you really going to defy me

238
00:14:01,279 --> 00:14:02,399
over this unknown apprentice?

239
00:14:02,399 --> 00:14:04,240
I never imagined the great Holder Li

240
00:14:04,240 --> 00:14:05,840
would disregard a patient's safety

241
00:14:05,840 --> 00:14:06,720
and start a fight in a ward.

242
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:07,120
Exactly.

243
00:14:08,200 --> 00:14:09,039
Director Ye.

244
00:14:09,840 --> 00:14:11,120
A mere apprentice

245
00:14:11,120 --> 00:14:13,000
dares to steal a patient from me, Li Xiangyang?

246
00:14:13,879 --> 00:14:15,240
Someone who breaks the rules like this,

247
00:14:15,240 --> 00:14:16,399
don't tell me you're trying to protect him?

248
00:14:16,399 --> 00:14:17,720
What if I am?

249
00:14:26,480 --> 00:14:27,039
Very well.

250
00:14:28,159 --> 00:14:30,399
So you're dead set on opposing me.

251
00:14:32,200 --> 00:14:33,759
Let me tell you,

252
00:14:33,759 --> 00:14:37,000
this apprentice is getting fired today.

253
00:14:38,399 --> 00:14:39,679
Who do you think you are?

254
00:14:40,039 --> 00:14:41,559
A mere Medicine Holder

255
00:14:41,559 --> 00:14:43,799
trying to dictate the personnel of Tianzi One?

256
00:14:45,440 --> 00:14:47,279
If you're not afraid of crossing the Li family,

257
00:14:48,039 --> 00:14:49,279
go ahead and try to stop me.

258
00:14:51,879 --> 00:14:53,000
You two.

259
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:54,960
I'm just a lowly apprentice.

260
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:55,679
There's really no need.

261
00:14:55,679 --> 00:14:56,519
No need at all.

262
00:14:57,360 --> 00:14:58,360
Thank you, Director Ye, for your appreciation.

263
00:14:59,399 --> 00:15:00,679
The world is vast.

264
00:15:00,679 --> 00:15:01,840
I can heal people anywhere.

265
00:15:02,480 --> 00:15:04,240
Director Ye, until we meet again.

266
00:15:05,600 --> 00:15:06,080
Holder Li.

267
00:15:06,080 --> 00:15:06,960
Take care of yourself.

268
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:08,320
Getting worked up isn't good for your health.

269
00:15:11,159 --> 00:15:13,200
Your kiddie smartwatch is ringing again.

270
00:15:13,200 --> 00:15:14,399
Remember to set it to vibrate next time.

271
00:15:19,440 --> 00:15:20,159
Xiangyang.

272
00:15:20,440 --> 00:15:21,000
Get lost!

273
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:22,879
Get lost!

274
00:15:31,759 --> 00:15:33,120
Where's the apprentice who just saved me?

275
00:15:34,000 --> 00:15:35,200
Why did he leave?

276
00:15:35,200 --> 00:15:36,600
He cured my illness,

277
00:15:36,600 --> 00:15:38,720
and I haven't even thanked him properly.

278
00:15:44,840 --> 00:15:45,879
Well...
